qd_sample

Source: R/qd_sample.R
qd_sample.Rd

qd_sample

qd_sample(categories, size)

Arguments

categories

a vector of valid QuickDraw category
size

a vector of number of rows to take from each category

Value

A tibble object that binds the sample data from all catgories.

Details

qd_sample() downloads QuickDraw data from multiple categories and take a sample from each category

Examples

qd_sample(c("octopus", "star"), 5)
